              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Passive Skill</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When your Burning Flame enters play:</span> After the next time either side uses a Skill, trigger 1 instance of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame's</span> End of Round effect. (Twice per Round)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/376d809c0de41d4b9c23cfceb8f433ab_1076379736879234361.png",
