                  }
                ],
                "title": "Lumidouce Case: Level 1"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span> to all opponents.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3227196376172976987.png",
                "key": "Lumidouce Case: Level 3",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/3d09272d15b07fd9eeb6b56453fcb8e8_7222425668536260108.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Lumidouce Case: Level 3"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_5191415200632622662.png",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Burning Flame</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span>: 1 (Can stack. Max 2 stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_2006739367802506657.png",
